<exercise id="fs-idm28148800">
<problem id="fs-idm88744080">
<para id="fs-idp27652976">From their positions in the periodic table, arrange the atoms in each of the following series in order of increasing electronegativity:</para>
<para id="fs-idp63429168">(a) C, F, H, N, O</para>
<para id="fs-idp19767520">(b) Br, Cl, F, H, I</para>
<para id="fs-idp256954784">(c) F, H, O, P, S</para>
<para id="fs-idp288482688">(d) Al, H, Na, O, P</para>
<para id="fs-idp249303488">(e) Ba, H, N, O, As</para>
</problem>
